	  <h2 itemprop="headline"><b>Devangshu Datta:</b> Explaining Delhi's polls - and bets</h2>
	  <h3 itemprop="alternativeHeadline"></h3>
	  <span itemprop="description">At the time of writing, the Delhi Assembly elections could yield three results. Some opinion polls give AAP a majority in the 70-seat Assembly, while other polls favour BJP</span>
